page.title: 01Agriculture some woodland
page.content:
Cereal growing, area with some livestock (mostly sheep) contains Poultry Farm 12000 bird size and dog and cat boarding kennels.
Main settlment Prestery Candover population 500 with sub settlemtn of Bradley and Asford and farm settlemtn at Nutly on Youdsmere,total population under 1000.
Whole area largely in single agri- cultural sporting estate ownership with two significant other land holdings remainder mainly residential holdings of signal cottages, occuped by Commuters and Retired folk
